# Follow the steps below to break root password for RHCSA Exam

Step 1. Power up/reboot the server and interupt the grub
Step 2. Select the the kernel to break the root password on
Step 3. preess e to edit the grup
Step 4. Go to the end of line linux16 and append rd.break and press ctrl + X
Step 5. Mount -o remount,rw /sysroot
Step 6. chroot /sysroot
Step 7. passswd root
Step 8. enter the root passwd twice
Step 9. touch /.autorelable
Step 10 exit
Step 11. exit again and wait for the server to reboot
